PortSystem 1.0
name             gob1
version          1.0.12
categories       devel
maintainers      toby@opendarwin.org
description      preprocessor for making GTK+ 1 objects with inline C
long_description \
	Old 1.0 version of gob for making GTK+ 1 (with \
	some support for GTK+ 2) objects.
